==Trivia==
*When attempting to use the fairy ring network without completion of the [[Lumbridge & Draynor Diary#Elite|elite Lumbridge & Draynor diary]], a [[dramen staff]], or a [[lunar staff]], the message, "''The fairy rings only work for those who wield fairy magic.''", appears.
*If the player has trapped themselves at a location only accessible by the fairy ring network, they may teleport back to Zanaris without a dramen or lunar staff regardless of if they have the elite Lumbridge & Draynor diary completed.
*When using a fairy ring any item equipped in the off-hand slot will momentarily disappear.
*Prior to the [[Update:Diverse Dungeons|Diverse Dungeons]] update, fairy ring code {{Fairycode|DJR}} teleported the player to [[Sinclair Mansion]] (west).
